Package org.sd.extract.filter

Interface Summary
Filter Marker interface for determing whether to filter input.
Filterable Interface for objects that can be filtered.
 

Class Summary
Filterer Utility class to apply a sequence of filters.
FilterUtil Utility class for applying common filter operations.
InputStreamFilterWrapper Abstract class for wrapping an input stream for filtering.
StringFilterWrapper Abstract class for wrapping a string for filtering.
UrlFilterWrapper Abstract class for wrapping a url string for filtering.
